('c5dd2109-d85b-5b0d-ae18-aa9cb580ee8a', 1, 'owner_age_proxy_rpls_tenure', 'negative', NULL, 'Senior RPLS DONALD HOLDER (TBPELS license #5266) granted 1998-06-12 → 28yr tenure. TX RPLS requires 4yr college + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + state exam (typically earned at age 28-35); est. owner age ~58.', 'tbpels_rpls_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
